
The purpose of the paper is to present the realization of zzso Project by a group of Centers of Medicine of Work in zzso within the project zzso Healthy zzso The study was carried out during zzso among the employees of the plants operating in the town of zzso The study focused on: comprehensive medical examinations performed by the physicians of occupational medicine in zzso with other specialist consultants, blood sampling with particular emphasis on the level of cholesterol, zzso and zzso The examinations allowed an early detection of diseases and appropriate treatment as well as health promotion and health education among the employees of the institution in zzso 

